---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — EmpowerX3"
  description="EmpowerX3 Terms of Service governing the use of our website and services, including medical disclaimer, user conduct, intellectual property, and limitation of liability."
  og={{
    title: "Terms of Service — EmpowerX3",
    description: "EmpowerX3 Terms of Service governing the use of our website and services.",
    image: "https://empowerx3.com/empower-logo-full.webp",
    type: "website"
  }}
  canonical="https://empowerx3.com/terms"
  noindex={true}
  schemaPageType="home"
  schemaBreadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: 'https://empowerx3.com/' },
    { name: 'Terms of Service', url: 'https://empowerx3.com/terms' }
  ]}
>

  <!-- ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative bg-stone-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-5" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 text-center">
      <p class="text-gold-500 font-heading font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6 text-cream-100 leading-tight">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Please read these terms carefully before using EmpowerX3.com and our services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Terms Content ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-16 text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">

      <!-- 1. Introduction -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to EmpowerX3.com (the "Site"). These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the Site, including any content, functionality, and services offered on or through the Site. By accessing or using the Site, you agree to be bound by these Terms and our <a href="/privacy" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>. If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the Site.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 2. Use of the Site -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">2. Use of the Site</h2>
        <p>You may use the Site only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You agree not to use the Site:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4 ml-4">
          <li>In any way that violates any applicable federal, state, local, or international law or regulation.</li>
          <li>For the purpose of exploiting, harming, or attempting to exploit or harm minors in any way.</li>
          <li>To transmit, or procure the sending of, any advertising or promotional material without our prior written consent.</li>
          <li>To impersonate or attempt to impersonate EmpowerX3, an EmpowerX3 employee, another user, or any other person or entity.</li>
          <li>To engage in any other conduct that restricts or inhibits anyone's use or enjoyment of the Site, or which, as determined by us, may harm EmpowerX3 or users of the Site or expose them to liability.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- 3. Intellectual Property -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>The Site and its entire contents, features, and functionality (including but not limited to all information, software, text, displays, images, video, and audio, and the design, selection, and arrangement thereof), are owned by EmpowerX3, its licensors, or other providers of such material and are protected by United States and international copyright, trademark, patent, trade secret, and other intellectual property or proprietary rights laws.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 4. User Contributions -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">4. User Contributions</h2>
        <p>The Site may contain comment sections, forums, or other interactive features that allow users to post content ("User Contributions"). Any User Contributions you post to the Site will be considered non-confidential and non-proprietary. By posting, you grant us a royalty-free, perpetual, irrevocable, non-exclusive, worldwide license to use, copy, modify, distribute, and display your User Contributions for any purpose.</p>
        <p>You represent and warrant that your User Contributions comply with these Terms and do not violate the rights of any third party.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 5. Medical Disclaimer -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">5. Medical Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="font-medium text-gold-400 mb-4">IMPORTANT: PLEASE READ THIS SECTION CAREFULLY.</p>
        <p>The information, content, and services provided on this Site are for educational and informational purposes only and are not intended as medical advice. The Site does not provide medical diagnosis, treatment, or advice. Nothing on this Site should be considered a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</p>
        <p>Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on this Site.</p>
        <p>EmpowerX3 and Gary Brandt are not licensed medical doctors. The programs, protocols, and recommendations described on this Site are based on personal experience, longevity principles, and general wellness information. Results vary by individual. There are no guarantees of specific outcomes.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 6. Services and Programs -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">6. Services and Programs</h2>
        <p>EmpowerX3 offers wellness coaching, longevity protocols, and access to the ExoPod cellular recovery system. These services are not medical treatments and are not covered by health insurance. All programs require a signed waiver and completion of a health questionnaire prior to participation.</p>
        <p>By purchasing or enrolling in any EmpowerX3 program, you acknowledge that you have read and understood the risks involved and voluntarily assume them. EmpowerX3 reserves the right to refuse service to anyone at any time.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 7. Payments and Refunds -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">7. Payments and Refunds</h2>
        <p>All purchases are processed through secure third-party payment processors. We do not store your full credit card information on our servers.</p>
        <p>Refund policies vary by program and are disclosed at the time of purchase. Generally, digital products and coaching programs are non-refundable once access has been granted. ExoPod session packages may have specific cancellation policies. Please review the specific terms for your purchase.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 8. Links to Third-Party Sites -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">8. Links to Third-Party Sites</h2>
        <p>The Site may contain links to third-party websites or resources. We have no control over the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites. You acknowledge and agree that we are not responsible or liable for any content, products, or services on or available from such websites. Use of third-party sites is at your own risk.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 9. Disclaimer of Warranties -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>YOUR USE OF THE SITE IS AT YOUR SOLE RISK. THE SITE IS PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS, WITHOUT ANY WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. EMPOWERX3 DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THE SITE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, TIMELY, SECURE, OR ERROR-FREE, OR THAT DEFECTS WILL BE CORRECTED.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 10. Limitation of Liability -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>IN NO EVENT SHALL EMPOWERX3, ITS OFFICERS, DIRECTORS, EMPLOYEES, OR AGENTS BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING WITHOUT LIMITATION, LOSS OF PROFITS, DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE LOSSES, RESULTING FROM (A) YOUR ACCESS TO OR USE OF OR INABILITY TO ACCESS OR USE THE SITE; (B) ANY CONDUCT OR CONTENT OF ANY THIRD PARTY ON THE SITE; OR (C) ANY CONTENT OBTAINED FROM THE SITE.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 11. Indemnification -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">11. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>You agree to defend, indemnify, and hold harmless EmpowerX3 and its officers, directors, employees, and agents from and against any claims, liabilities, damages, judgments, awards, losses, costs, expenses, or fees (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising out of or relating to your violation of these Terms or your use of the Site.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 12. Governing Law -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">12. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Texas, without regard to its conflict of law provisions. Any dispute arising under these Terms shall be resolved exclusively in the state or federal courts located in Travis County, Texas.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 13. Changes to the Terms -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">13. Changes to the Terms</h2>
        <p>We may revise these Terms at any time by updating this page. The "Last Updated" date at the top of this page indicates when the most recent changes were made. Your continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- 14. Contact Us -->
      <article>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">14. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
        <address class="not-italic mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          EmpowerX3<br>
          Email: <a href="mailto:gary@empowerx3.com" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">gary@empowerx3.com</a><br>
          Phone: <a href="tel:+15127999765" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">(512) 799-9765</a>
        </address>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Contact CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-900 border-y border-stone-700">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-cream-100 mb-4">Questions About These Terms?</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-400 mb-8">Reach out — we're happy to clarify.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-gold-500 text-stone-950 font-semibold hover:bg-gold-400 transition-colors">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>